message.entry: Expected input image to be a 2-D or 3-D real-valued, non-sparse gpuArray with underlying class uint8, uint16, uint32, int8, int16, int32, logical, single or double.
Expected method name to be a non-empty string or character vector. Only 'euclidean' is supported on the GPU.
BWDIST is not supported for gpuArray's with more than (2^32-1) elements.
